    <briefdescription>
<para>Linkable loadable extension symbol definitions. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This file provides a set of macros and structures for defining and exporting symbols from the base image to extensions and vice versa, so that proper linking can be done between the two entities. </para>
